  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stranded in the Norwegian mountains after a bus crash, unity is your only hope. Work together to find shelter, scavenge for resources, and conquer the elements. Surviving this ordeal requires teamwork, pooling skills and supplies. Trust your companions as you face the challenges ahead, knowing that only by collaborating can you make it out alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this treacherous game of survival, a killer lurks among your friends. Trust becomes a delicate balance. Assess motives and actions carefully as you navigate this deadly scenario. Will your companions be allies or adversaries? Unmasking the killer is a matter of life and death, but who can you truly trust?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Search the wilderness for vital resources in your battle for survival. Collect what you can, for every item is precious. Share your finds with fellow survivors, pooling resources for meals, warmth, and sustenance. The key lies in collaboration, making the most of what you discover together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nourishment, hydration, rest, and warmth are essential for survival. Find food to sustain yourselves, secure water sources, take moments to rest and recharge, and protect against the biting cold. These pillars of survival will determine your fate in this harsh mountain landscape.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/68dc130f84fca17a5185e76cecd5ce56.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stranded in the Norwegian mountains after a bus crash, unity is your only hope. Work together to find shelter, scavenge for resources, and conquer the elements. Surviving this ordeal requires teamwork, pooling skills and supplies. Trust your companions as you face the challenges ahead, knowing that only by collaborating can you make it out alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/501acc9fbd336c408e078f6090bb1fc5.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this treacherous game of survival, a killer lurks among your friends. Trust becomes a delicate balance. Assess motives and actions carefully as you navigate this deadly scenario. Will your companions be allies or adversaries? Unmasking the killer is a matter of life and death, but who can you truly trust?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/39830f76dc697e85fa1cc8910babfaf5.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Search the wilderness for vital resources in your battle for survival. Collect what you can, for every item is precious. Share your finds with fellow survivors, pooling resources for meals, warmth, and sustenance. The key lies in collaboration, making the most of what you discover together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.poster.avif?t=1741709386\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.webm?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382190/extras/2fb09980788e64cb1a6b5c7c7fad64aa.mp4?t=1741709386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nourishment, hydration, rest, and warmth are essential for survival. Find food to sustain yourselves, secure water sources, take moments to rest and recharge, and protect against the biting cold. These pillars of survival will determine your fate in this harsh mountain landscape.",
